# Technology Stack

## Backend
- **Elixir/Phoenix**: Primary application framework
- **PostgreSQL**: Relational database for data persistence
- **Ecto**: Database wrapper and query generator
  - Schema definitions for data structures
  - Migrations for database changes
  - Query composition for complex data retrieval

## Frontend
- **Phoenix LiveView**: Server-rendered dynamic UI
  - Real-time user interactions without JavaScript
  - LiveComponents for reusable UI elements
  - Minimal client-side code
- **TailwindCSS**: Utility-first CSS framework

## Deployment
- **fly.io**: Cloud deployment platform (free tier)
- **Docker**: Containerization for deployment

## Development Considerations
- Maintain zero cost by staying within free tier limits
- Follow Elixir/Phoenix/Ecto best practices for maintainable code
- Use appropriate database indexing and query optimization
- Optimize LiveView for performance
